				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Omens of War expansion adds new AA<a name="65293"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Oct 1 04 11:56 AM</span></td>
