				<td colspan="2"><span>
<br />
By my random calculation, the max level of Dance of Blades, will give you a 100% chance to dual wield, and a 100% chance to double attack.... that is, 4 attacks per round, always, for the duration of the disc... assuming you have Harmonious Attak 5.
<br />

<br />
HA 5 gives you a 20% chance to DA.
<br />

<br />
DoB level 1 gives +200% chance to DA.    That would be a 60% chance total to DA.
<br />

<br />
DoB level 2 gives +300% chance to DA.    That would be 80% chance to DA.
<br />

<br />
DoB level 3 gives +400% chance to DA.   That would be 100% chance to DA.
<br />

<br />
So it could amount to a little burst of damage.
<br />
</span></td>
